15,01The Gypsy Affair

15,01Beware, beware
15,01The gypsies at the gate
15,01Their gossamer scarves
15,01And lively gait
15,01As true love stands by
15,01They steal you away
15,01With their bewitching dance
15,01And enchanting play.

15,01Beware, beware
15,01The gypsies at the gate
15,01The seductive goddess
15,01That refuses to wait.
15,01Forget your conscience,
15,01Forget the one that loves you
15,01Know only the passion
15,01The gypsy and the dew.

15,01Beware, beware
15,01The gypsies at the gate
15,01What you had, you've lost
15,01True love turned to hate.
15,01In the morning
15,01The gypsies are gone
15,01To that place between
15,01The lust and the dawn.

15,01Beware, beware
15,01The gypsies are waiting there...

